abstract: News media coverage of the Occupy Wall Street protests has increased since demonstrators clashed with the police, and is beginning to rival coverage given to Tea Party protests in 2009.
snippet: News media coverage of the Occupy Wall Street protests has increased since demonstrators clashed with the police, and is beginning to rival coverage given to Tea Party protests in 2009.
lead_paragraph: The Occupy Wall Street protests, by design, began with little in the way of concrete goals or strategy.

headline.main: Police Clashes Spur Coverage of Wall Street Protests
